              <title>Free financial modeling training</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/8861</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/8861</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.wallstreetmojo.com/free-financial-modeling-training-course/">Financial modeling</a> is the task of building an abstract representation (a model) of a real world financial situation. This is a mathematical model designed to represent (a simplified version of) the performance of a financial asset or portfolio of a business, project, or any other investment. Financial modeling is a general term that means different things to different users; the reference usually relates either to accounting and corporate finance applications, or to quantitative finance applications.</p>
