<p>This is an innovation website. &nbsp;And I'm trying to set out ideas that raise issues for new development. &nbsp;Hence the questions. &nbsp;You can get into the conversation using the 'contribution' box below. &nbsp;Or e-mail me by finding 'bill' on the home page of <a title="café" href="http://www.hihohiho.com" target="_self">the career-learning caf&eacute;</a>. &nbsp;We all need all the help we can get.</p>
<p style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->Dr Bill Law FRSA<br /><a title="café" href="http://www.hihohiho.com" target="_self">the career-learning caf&eacute;<br /></a>08/11/2013</p>
