              <description><![CDATA[<p>Prompted by the mad cap videos by @mweller and co for their forthcoming presentations at the JISC online conference I've decided to create this cloud to share and discuss ideas around how universities of the future might look like. Here are some questions to stimulate the debate:</p>
<ul>
<li>In a world where increasingly both contetn and expertise is freely available, what does a university offer?</li>
